summary.short: A customer, Javier, calls Qualia Auto Body to inquire about his GMC Terrain's status. The representative, Jackie, confirms that the vehicle is being finished and offers to transfer him to a higher management member. The customer asks the agent to put pressure on the insurance company and get the vehicle back by the end of the day. The agent explains that they are submitting everything they need, but sometimes it doesn't move things faster. The customer is waiting for a response from Robert, and the representative will reach out to him to provide an update.
